JRFramework is a simple way to start a Java Swing and Hibernate project with table and forms.
This beta version have a example within the project is Actores Sakila database of Mysql, to teste and run you must have first to install Sakila database, can be downloaded from MySql web site.
Realease version will not have the example within the source code but beside.

Libraries:
	Hibernate 3
	JDK 1.7
	Mysql-connecte-java-5.1.18


packages:
	 info.joaorebelo.JRFramework
	 * Main class
	 * Default Layout

	info.joaorebelo.JRjavaUtils.table
	* Class to contruct the tables

	info.joaorebelo.JRjavaUtils.ui
	* Utilities


	

